In the new version we present a completely new design in two color schemes: dark and light! Added the function that you asked and waited: “Who blocked me”. The “Engagement Rate” indicator is now available on other people's profiles also.

Check how interesting your friends' profiles are, analyze your subscribers, track who blocked you and more! Enjoy using!
